title: Lil Boosie-Complete Discography(36 Albums;Studio,Mixtapes,Single
description:
This is the complete Lil Boosie Discography!!!Anything Else is fan made!!!!  Only a Couple Songs off the Lava House Mixtape are missing due to quality issues!!!!!  A Must Have For All Boosie Fans!!!!! 

Contains Following:

Studio albums
2000: Youngest Of Da Camp
2002: For My Thugz
2006: Bad Azz
2009: Superbad: The Return of Boosie Bad Azz
2010: Incarcerated



Collaboration Albums

2000: C-Loc Present Camp III: Thug Brothas (with Concentration Camp)
2003: Pimp C Present: Ghetto Stories (with Webbie)
2004: Gangsta Musik (with Webbie)
2004: C-Loc Present Camp IV: Thuggin' From The Inside (with Concentration Camp)[35]
2007: Trill Entertainment Presents: Survival of the Fittest (with Foxx, Webbie and Trill Fam)
2010: Trill Entertainment Presents: All or Nothing (with Foxx, Webbie and Trill Fam)


Mixtapes

2002: Boosie 2002 (Advance)
2004: Trill Azz Mixtape
2004: Trill Azz Mixes II
2004: Bad Ass 2004
2006: Bad Azz Mixtape Vol.1
2006: Streetz Iz Mine (Hosted by DJ Drama)
2007: Bad Azz Mixtape Vol.2
2008: Da Beginning'
2008: 4th Of July Bash
2008: Lil Boosie Presents: Da Click
2009: The Return Of Mr. Wipe Me Down
2009: The 25th Hour (Hosted by DJ Folk & DJ Got Now)
2009: Da Click: ''Street Kingz
2009: Thug Passion
2010: Shouldve Been My Beatz
2010: Gone Til December



Collaboration Mixtapes

2004: Both Sides of the Track (with South Coast Coalition)
2005: United We Stand, Divided We Fall (with Lava House)
2005: Street Code (with Pat Lowrenzo)
2007: Street Tapes Vol.1 (with Lava House)
2009: Category 7: Bad Azz Hurricane (with Hurricane Chris)
2009: Untouchable (with LoLa Monroe)
2010: 22504 (with B.G.)
2011: Hit After Hit 3 (with Quick)
2012: My Brother's Keeper (with Money Bagz & Quick)
2012: Under Investigation (with Ray Vicks)



Compilation Mixtapes

2010: Unbreakable (with C-Loc)
